column5: got out at 1:00pm  thursday afternoon for  the day not the best time to go steelheading but take what you can get when you can got the first one on the first drift and it ended to be a good afternoon after all went 6 for 10 on the day
why do my photo's keep doing this I got it from photobucket and made them thumbnails?
You don't need to make them thumbnails if they are already on Photobucket.  Just link in the  tags of each picture one after the other.
